I’ve been drawing a lot these last days! I’m really glad because I’ve been improving my art skills lately. I still have a long way to go, but I’m still very happy about it

Today I made a drawing of snufkin, one of “The Moomins” characters. I really enjoy the series. I recommend watching the different adaptations, they’re amazing.
